If you are using version 5 of the Spring web MVC then you will have to use the version 5 of Hibernate core and not the version 6. So change the following:

    &lt;dependency&gt;
      &lt;groupId&gt;org.hibernate&lt;/groupId&gt;
      &lt;artifactId&gt;hibernate-core&lt;/artifactId&gt;
      &lt;version&gt;6.0.0.CR1&lt;/version&gt;
    &lt;/dependency&gt;
to:

    &lt;dependency&gt;
      &lt;groupId&gt;org.hibernate&lt;/groupId&gt;
      &lt;artifactId&gt;hibernate-core&lt;/artifactId&gt;
      &lt;version&gt;5.3.27.Final&lt;/version&gt;
    &lt;/dependency&gt;

Also, now you will have to change the imports from jakarta.persistence to javax.persistence. And instead of using

    SelectionQuery&lt;PracticeSessionDto&gt; query = (SelectionQuery&lt;PracticeSessionDto&gt;) hibernate_session.createSelectionQuery(fetch_todo_query);

you will have to use

    Query query = hibernate_session.createQuery(fetch_todo_query);
Hope this helps.

